://na.cx/i/y05k1s7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy05k1s7.jpg&h=289609e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n走之前幾個月<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cen7zhK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcen7zhK.jpg&h=04cb7eb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家喺彩虹橋食緊燒肉<br />\n好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773bb8e6ec0fa21854c0039e4aae3d121727feab","tid":11144,"uid":741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:57:32.000Z","msg":"好想養狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd600bc070ba83328181b4462795ca2facb7872","tid":11144,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪真係有&quot;柴距離&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日本節目講<br />\n柴犬會同主人保持一段距離<br />\n叫又唔係好睬人<br />\n反而同其他屋企人親密啲</blockquote><br />\n柴犬不嬲個個叫佢都唔采人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我個隻就超鍾意我老豆<br />\n老豆成日係房我隻柴柴就係佢門口係咁吠到佢出黎唯只<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我一出門口就成日比佢咬我隻腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc8e320c3d28252d9c9b60764debb551784bc06","tid":11144,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:15:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪話柴犬好固執？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，叫佢唔好咬就佢篇要咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到屋企d角﹑牆紙﹑沙發全部都一個個窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4fa3887d3200a0ef535b46d1482d414804df36","tid":11144,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:15:46.000Z",